                 ; isEquivalence = record  { refl   = Œª _ ‚Üí refl
                                           ; sym    = Œª h x ‚Üí sym (h x)
                                           ; trans  = Œª g h x ‚Üí trans (g x)(h x) }}

\end{code}

Next we define *evaluation of a term* in an environment `œÅ`, interpreted in the algebra `ùë®`.

\begin{code}

